A lot of data show that therapeutic education is beneficial for diabetic patients.

 In the French jails, there are very few programs of therapeutic education while this population is usually precarious with no access at care sector before the jail.

 The purpose of this study is to determinate if the therapeutic education of the diabetic patients is possible in the Paris jail "La Sante".

